        "text_PJxJEe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>You received The Sun because your clarity and joy are becoming accessible again. Things will feel simpler and confusion is lifting like fading mist. You may observe more honesty in relationships, more confidence in decisions, and an overall lighter mood. <\/h3><h3>This card appears to those whose alignment is slowly but surely replacing struggle.  Your happiness can exist without justification. You are allowed to experience what feels easy. <\/h3><h3>You must remain open and invite warmth and opportunities to stand out. Life will be more direct, and with undemanding grace, you will feel more grounded than ever. <br\/><br\/>On Love<\/h3><p>You will have the most honest, joyful relationships. Always be clear about what you want from the relationship, communicate your thoughts plainly. If you love someone, tell them. <\/p><h3>On Health<\/h3><p>The time for strong vitality. Keep moving your body everyday and allow sunlight to restore energy.  <\/p><h3>On Money \/ Career<\/h3><p>Success, recognition, and progress are all going to follow you like a shadow. Accept new challenges with confidence and deliver with spirit. <\/p><p>How to work with this energy<\/p><p>You are the light in every room. Believe it, and thoroughly enjoy it!<br\/><br\/>Recommended products<\/p><ol><li>Sunday Rituals Hair Repair & Growth Oil – Vitality & shine<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Squeeze the Day Bag Charm (Lemon) – Joy & brightness<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Cross Braided Essentials Handbag – Green Mountains Edition – Fun & thriving<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Enamel pin (Lavender) – Sun-loving<br\/><br\/><\/li><\/ol><p>You can find these in our pop-up booth at Night At Orchard, along the outdoor pathway between Ngee Ann City & Ion Orchard between 26-28 Dec, 3pm onwards <\/p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
